{"tid":1224702,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"拒做「極權龜」！ 《蘋果日報》明日送「自由hi」海報","createTime":"2019-06-15T04:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T13:11:29.000Z","uid":212249,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4fca01bb588e3e3dca010454fb57c0300e52d478","tid":1224702,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190615/large/1560572728_d412.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190615%2Flarge%2F1560572728_d412.jpg&h=b9aea477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.9遊行103萬人逼爆港島，大批遊行人士在維園等候近5小時才能起步，但港府仍拒絕撤回條例，激發更多人上街，最終6月12日的警方暴力清場，民間人權陣線宣佈明日（6月16日）再次舉行「反送中」大遊行，以香港人的一雙腳、一把聲音，向極權說不。插畫家阿塗設計了一款「寧做自由Hi，不做極權龜」海報，明天（6月16日）隨報《蘋果》附送，另5,000份下午一點起於皇室堡及興發街附近派發，派完即止。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140f70221b6a505342f78b0eebfc352fb33a16d2","tid":1224702,"uid":123115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:39:31.000Z","msg":"原意係好<br />\n<br />\n但有啲膠化聽日個遊行<br />\n<br />\n目標要清楚<br />\n<br />\n撒 （永久暫緩） 同埋 放人"},{"pid":"cdef36447eda12f6eb1ac3aaf998093fe292f3c0","tid":1224702,"uid":191989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:11:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}